About Version 2:
 1. The THRESHOLD variable was decreased to 320 account for a closer value to the specific wet soil value 283, which accounts for errors
 2. Featuring longer 40 second intervals of the pump being on for better watering due to the Capacitive Moisture Sensor being located at the top
 3. The loop was also increased to being repeated 7 times, each 40 second intervals
 4. These new features promote more accurate sensing and watering based on the current state of moisture in the soil
 5. The LCD_I2C is now better controled, with longer intervals of showing text and values, allowing for the person to see what is happening
